## Package Manager
- **Always use yarn** as the package manager, not npm
- Use `yarn add` instead of `npm install`
- Use `yarn dev` instead of `npm run dev`
- Use `yarn build` instead of `npm run build`
- Use `yarn lint` instead of `npm run lint`
- Use `yarn start` instead of `npm start`

## Project Context
This is a Next.js 15 project for Pyre Sauna + Cold Plunge, a wellness facility coming to Richmond, VA. The project uses:
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- shadcn/ui components
- Custom fonts (PPNeueMontreal and PPFraktionMono)

## Code Style
- Use TypeScript for all new files
- Follow the existing component structure in `src/components/`
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling
- Maintain responsive design patterns
- Follow the established naming conventions

## File Organization
- Components go in `src/components/`
- UI components go in `src/components/ui/`
- Utilities go in `src/lib/`
- Images go in `public/images/`
- Fonts go in `public/fonts/`
- Logos go in `public/logos/` 